FTDNFkdL.jpg&h=a73844ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T23:26:00.000Z","msg":"故意不吃，因為可以消耗體內積聚的熱量。<br />\n間竭性斷食。晚餐後不再進食，不宵夜，不早餐，沒有上午茶，直至到午餐。總共16小時斷食。<br />\n我已經減了4公斤。連運動也沒有就可以-4公斤。"},{"pid":"db90a054d805ddc69fa470d3f54cfc9b5d434558","tid":1673732,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T23:36:32.000Z","msg":"我每朝七點食晚飯<br />\n晏晝一兩點宵夜，夜晚先lunch"},{"pid":"57f2ec9fc0e3cf2faddbfdf2ac92b9dd5a445d6e","tid":1673732,"uid":276839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T00:33:26.000Z","msg":"我唔會空肚食早餐。"},{"pid":"ff40fc6c9e838fd7e1a5853f34659aabb9f4f6c0","tid":1673732,"uid":204917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T00:42:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}